The setup comprises devices like the controlled press originally designed inhouse as described in [31], but later modified for speed, force, and controllability in Fig. 4
                            (see more information in Table 5
                           ), type K (NiCr-Ni) thermocouples with configuration_1 for temperature sensing, FLIR E96 thermal camera for thermal videoing, Canon XA30 for image videoing, and DAQ for logging parameters like voltage and temperature at 10 Hz.
